Planning for startup adventure


Card is an empty shell
Function to inject data into the card
Function to add or subtract value (users) from the global object
Managing options

[
{
	title: "my card",
	description: "card desc",
	options: [
		{
			title: 'get investment money',
			value: '1000'
		},
		{
			title: 'take out a second mortgage'
			value: -500,
		}
	]
}
]

